      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for its next big adventure! It has been super reliable and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. It\u2019s been well-loved, kept clean, and runs like a charm. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I just know you're going to have a blast behind the wheel. Come by and take it for a spin!",
