    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) providing adaptable compression and rebound settings. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the mechanical longevity of this analog masterpiece. The exterior retains a clean aesthetic with minor road rash consistent with its status, while the subframe and bushings remain sound for aggressive cornering transitions.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
