    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable and well-presented car. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though I want to be transparent about a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the lower rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the leather seats are supple with no rips, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All interior electronics, including the infotainment system, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent oil change, new air filters, and a tire rotation performed just last month. The engine idles smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It comes with a clean title, two sets of keys, and a thick folder of service receipts to give the next owner total peace of mind. This is a solid, honest vehicle that has been genuinely cared for.",
      "price": 32500.0,
