    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable daily driver, and it\u2019s honestly such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-cared for over the years. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth ride that\u2019s ready for any adventure, this is the one for you! It\u2019s got plenty of life left and is just waiting for its next owner to jump in and enjoy. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
